						               													<description>Launch the Crystal (Mini) is a game where players have to try to save the planet by launching the dangerous unstable Nuclear Crystal away from the earth, into deep space. This is a board game of individual players each pitted against each other to try to win the crown of honor prize for being the first to launch the unstable Nuclear Crystal into space away from the earth.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Game is played on a board labelled from 1 to 100. The Board has four different colors going on each end labelled 1 to 100. The Game Board can switch color at a moment's notice thanks to Ability cards such as Earth Bending or Terraforming. When this happens, the number is switched to a different colored number. Players on 1 can be warped to 100 square, 90 square, or 10 square.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player is designated a Mutant Gene card as their special ability throughout the game. Tokens or Weapons are collected as a player progresses through the board. Tokens are used to buy Ability cards or activate Mutant Gene abilities while weapons are used in battle with other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A battle is conducted if a player lands on the same space as another player. There are three time capsule pieces in the game where if a player collects all of them, they are automatically warped to the 100 square. They can lose a time capsule piece during a battle.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If a player lands on the 100 square, they must roll a 1 to successful launch the nuclear crystal into deep space and win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
